  "pluginNotes": {
    "textInjectionMethod": "none",
    "sizingConstraints": "Native Figma frame with image fill. Width/height explicit in spec.",
    "knownIssues": [
      "SAP Web UI Kit has no dedicated Image component — plugin renders as a native Figma frame with a rounded-rectangle placeholder fill (sapContent_Placeholderloading token) plus a stroke. Spec.props.src is documented but not fetched at build time; use Figma's Insert Image after build if a real image is needed."
    ]
